overview: Vanna is the personal assistant of a rich businessman. She manages all his current affairs for him, even the most personal ones, and doesn't count her hours. In appearance, she leads a perfect life. In reality, the pretty redhead is secretly in love with her boss and can't stand to see him spending his nights with a different girl every time... until now.  Katrina and Tommy live a passionate love story. Every day, both of them are doing everything ...
title: Stars 8
